								Collection First-Line Index</title>. New Haven: Beinecke Library, Yale
								University, 2005,  175, item D0034</bibref>
                     <bibref title="">Nelson (ed.), <title render="italic">Union First Line Index</title>. Mar. 2010. Folger Shakespeare
