                  </bibliography>
                  <scopecontent>
                     <p>Transcript, entitled <title render="doublequote">Hymn to adversity</title>,
								in <persname role="trc" normal="Forbes, James, 1749-1819">James
								Forbes</persname>' <title render="italic">Commonplace book,
								1766-1800</title>, vol. I "Poems on Several Occasions Collected
								from Different Authors", a manuscript collection of approximately
								150 poems and excerpts, primarily epitaphs and elegies, poems in praise
								of virtues, odes dedicated to women, and poems on nature and weather.
							</p>
                  </scopecontent>
